events.text: Hello, I would like to pass this material.
Hmmm, lemme check wait a second.

Yes, this is the material that the hint was conveying.
Congratulations! You passed the exam.
I'll give you a certificate as proof that you passed.

"The certificate before you grants passage to the chamber.
Go forth and test your knowledge, young one,
for it is only with preparation that you can embark
on the journey that awaits you."
